			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Trovit is a dynamic and international company totally focused on technology. We are the leading search engine for classifieds in Europe and Latin America, and our objective is to become the major global search engine in the world.</p>
<p>
We use the most innovative technologies in our area, with high traffic and a global philosophy. We are looking for startup minded people, who love new technologies and are eager to learn and contribute to a highly creative and collaborative engineering department, which is one of the most outstanding in Spain.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
At the moment we are looking for a person to join the Systems Administration department that manages the servers infrastructure and our own applications, making sure that our search engine runs smoothly with no interruptions.</p>
<p>
<strong>His/her job will basically consist in&hellip;</strong><br />
- Maintain own network infrastructure and servers that underpin the web search engine and other company applications.<br />
- Propose innovative and technologically leading solutions to support the company growth.<br />
- Ensure the availability, security and performance of the platform, eliminating points of failure and bottlenecks.<br />
- Work closely with the development teams to implement scalable and robust solutions.<br />
- On-call support.</p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements:</strong><br />
- Passionate about his/her work and with a clear R&amp;D focus.<br />
- Professional, proactive and with spirit of improvement that enjoys taking on challenges and responsibilities.<br />
- Analytical skills and creativity to solve problems in alternative ways.<br />
- Knowledge of open source software and Linux operating systems.<br />
- Knowledge of technologies such as: Apache, MySQL.<br />
- Programming of shell scripts, Perl, PHP.<br />
- Thorough knowledge of network protocols: TCP / IP, DNS, DHCP.<br />
- Management of firewalls, load balancers, routers, switches.<br />
- Fluent in English (technical reading).</p>
<p>
<strong>Desirable:</strong><br />
- Experience with high-traffic web environment.<br />
- Knowledge of technologies such as: Nginx, Redis and NoSQL solutions, Hadoop, Xen.<br />
- Knowledge of Amazon Web Services (EC2 and S3).<br />
- Configuration management with Puppet.</p>
<p>
<strong>What you will get:</strong><br />
- A professional career according to your qualifications, experience, professional potential and expectations.<br />
- Training from day one, attending conferences, fairs, etc.<br />
- Social benefits: lunch vouchers, medical insurance, discounts, etc.<br />
- Salary according to experience and value that you can bring to the team.</p>
<p>
Trovit is one of the most exciting startups in Europe and has a young and enthusiastic work environment. We offer everything you would expect from a startup, including free snacks and drinks, a game-room with all the consoles and a huge screen, after-office events, ski-trip, offsite events...</p>
<p>
We offer a competitive salary and many benefits, and we had been named one of the 50 Best Workplaces in Spain, according to Great Place to Work&reg; for 2011, 2012 and 2013.</p>
<p>
Come and help us create the best search engine for classifieds!</p>
